SAMIAJIJ MIAWPUKEK INDIAN RESERVE REMISSION ORDER - which provides for the
remission of income tax, other debts, corresponding interest and penalties
payable for the years 1985, 1986 and 1987 by members of the Miawpukek
Indian Band on income earned on those lands now known as the Samiajij
Miawpukek Indian Reserve in Newfoundland.
